<br>
I agree completely that durring the raid is a baaaaad time to do major changes like that, but after the raid send a tell and say &quot;hey, if you're on tomorrow can we talk? got a few questions and would take too long tonight&quot; I got noo probs with that! *hugs* all the better. I just honestly wish ANYone would have said something sooner.<br>
<br>
I cant really clarify on the black marble thing that dropped. All the gems collected usually go into a fund and when someone has a piece of armor and needs a couple jems they borrow from there. With Valo loot isn't rolled for, its distributed by 1 single, selfless and dedicated person. We all have our equipment listed on the site, she chooses which of us needs it best, though if no one needs it then the guests (from what I've seen) were more than welcome to put their name in for it. It's how I got my Ornate shield before I joined them.<br>
<br>
PS. As to the person that told me to get lost, heh... I politely told em I had just as much right to be there as they did.<br>
Response - &quot;oh and how do you figure that?&quot;<br>
Me - &quot;2 reasons, number one - my guild isn't in the rotation though I see your's is in ******** Alliance and is...<br>
Me - &quot;and second, I dont insult people in tells to get a better chance at winning something =P&quot;<br>
Me - &quot;and since I dont want any of the loot anyway I dont really care if you think I should be here or not&quot;<br>
Response - complete silence<br>
