The only stipulation on the CoG raids is that you adhere to the principles of the CoG, i.e. fun for all, no exclusions based on guild or not, unless mandated by another rule set (such as the KGC). Those who complain should try to run one... it will usually shut them up quicker than anything. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
